						<div class="postbody">Hello,
<br />
<br />Since I started here  I've used the .db style format for all my level data.  However, my recent project is quite big and doing this .db format has become quite a headache to manage.  I'm always getting confused on whats going on where after while.  I've spoke (well typed) with Tokumaru a bit and I believe it's time I started looking into writing my own level editor.  While I use C a lot, I've never attempted a level editor before and am having some issues getting started.  Any thoughts, ideas, possible graphic libraries I should use, etc to get me started would greatly be appreciated.</div>

